      -  below we rely on the fact that the Spanish stemmer turns all forms of
      -  estar, ser, haber back to the infinitive. In generating the stemmed
      -  stopword list we only really need to mention these infinitive forms.

estar          -  to be
haber          -  to have
ser            -  to be
tener          -  to have

